<%# HTML correspondiente a la pagina de about-us %>


<div class="about-me-container">

  <%# division correspondiente a la barra de navegacion %>
  <div class="navbar-container">
    <%# carta contenedora de botones de izquierda %>
    <div class="navbar-card-button">

      <div class="navbar-card-home">
        <button class="navbar-Home"><%= link_to "Home", home_path, class: "navbar-Home" %>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="navbar-card-about-me">
        <button class="navbar-about-me"><%= link_to "About", aboutme_path, class: "navbar-about-me" %>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="navbar-card-project">
        <button class="navbar-projects"><%= link_to "Projects", projects_path, class: "navbar-projects" %>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="navbar-card-contact">
        <button class="navbar-button-contact"><%= link_to "Contact", contact_path, class: "navbar-contact" %>
        </button>
      </div>

    </div>

    <%# carta contenedora de botones de idiomas %>
    <div class="navbar-right-card">
      <div class="dropdown">
        <button class="dropdown-toggle"><%= image_tag "united-kingdom.png" %> Language</button>
        <div class="dropdown-menu">
          <a href="/home" class="dropdown-item"><%= image_tag "united-kingdom.png" %> English</a>
          <a href="/home_esp" class="dropdown-item"><%= image_tag "spain.png" %> Spanish</a>
          <a href="/home_por" class="dropdown-item"><%= image_tag "brazil.png" %> Portuguese</a>
          <a href="/home_fra" class="dropdown-item"><%= image_tag "france.png" %> French</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

  <%# division correspondiente a la presentacion ENG %>
  <div class="about-me-presentation">
    <h2>As Web-Developpers</h2>
    <p>As full-stack web developers specialized in front-end development and backend, we possess a comprehensive
    skill set tailored towards crafting engaging and interactive user interfaces. With a solid foundation
    in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, we've honed my abilities to create visually stunning and responsive web
    experiences that captivate users.</p>
    <p>Having a bootcamp intensive training at Le Wagon in Lille, France, we've been equipped with cutting-edge
    techniques and best practices in web development. Our expertise extends to leveraging various
    libraries and frameworks to streamline development processes
    and enhance the functionality of web applications.</p>
    <p>In addition to our technical proficiency, we bring a creative mindset and a keen eye for design
    aesthetics to every project we undertake. Whether it's implementing complex UI components, optimizing
    performance, or ensuring cross-browser compatibility, we thrive on overcoming challenges and delivering
    solutions that exceed client expectations.</p>
    <p>Our dedication to staying abreast of industry trends and continuously expanding our skills set ensures
    that we remain at the forefront, front-end development and back-end. With a passion for innovation and a commitment to
    excellence, we are poised to contribute effectively to projects that demand top-tier front-end development
    expertise.</p>
  </div>



</div>
